UNITED STATES ex rel. Rachael SLAKMANIENE and Another, Relators-Appeliants, v. Henry H. CURRAN, as Commissioner, etc., Respondent-Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 19, 1926.) No. 359. John M. Lyons, of New York City, for appellants.. Emory R. Buckner, U. S. Atty. (N. R. Margold, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH, and HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed in open court.
